# PR Review Comment Replies

When asked to respond to PR review comments:

- Always reply in the original review thread/comment, not only in a general PR comment.
- If the feedback was applied, include the commit SHA or commit URL that contains the change.
- If the feedback was not applied, explain the reason briefly in the same thread.
